@Ticketmatic
#take health 1
#take health 54
#give ammo 120
/i/i/i/i
(After sprinting a few blocks, Burns
reaches the locked doors of the Rederring
Civic Theater.)

Burns:
(gasps) Open the door! It's an emergency!

Ticketmatic:
Hello, and welcome to the Rederring Civic
Theater. Tonight's performance -

Burns:
Let me speak to the manager!

Ticketmatic:
- of Iolanthe is sold out. If you wish
to reserve seats for -

Burns:
Let me speak to _any_ human being!

Ticketmatic:
- next week's performance, please call -

Burns:
This is hopeless. Maybe I can get in
by the fire escape.

(Burns runs into an alley by the side of
the theater.)

Ticketmatic:
(555) 1WE-CARE.
/i
Time to save your game.
#send blocker:free
#end

